  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "呂不韋者，陽翟大賈人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "往來販賤賣貴，家累千金。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Lü Buwei was a great merchant from Yangdi. He traveled trading, buying cheap selling dear, household accumulated thousand jin gold.",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "秦昭王四十年，太子死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "其四十二年，以其次子安國君為太子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "安國君有子二十餘人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "安國君有所甚愛姬，立以為正夫人，號曰華陽夫人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "華陽夫人無子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "安國君中男名子楚，子楚母曰夏姬，毋愛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "子楚為秦質子於趙。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "秦數攻趙，趙不甚禮子楚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Qin King Zhao fortieth year, crown prince died. His forty-second year, made his second son Anguo Jun crown prince. Anguo Jun had sons twenty plus persons. Anguo Jun had a much loved concubine, established as proper wife, titled Huayang Madame. Huayang Madame had no sons. Anguo Jun middle son named Zichu, Zichu mother called Xia Ji, not favored. Zichu served as Qin hostage in Zhao. Qin repeatedly attacked Zhao, Zhao not much honored Zichu.",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "子楚，秦諸庶孽孫，質於諸侯，車乘進用不饒，居處困，不得意。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "呂不韋賈邯鄲，見而憐之，曰「此奇貨可居」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "乃往見子楚，說曰：「吾能大子之門。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "子楚笑曰：「且自大君之門，而乃大吾門！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "呂不韋曰：「子不知也，吾門待子門而大。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "子楚心知所謂，乃引與坐，深語。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "呂不韋曰：「秦王老矣，安國君得為太子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "竊聞安國君愛幸華陽夫人，華陽夫人無子，能立適嗣者獨華陽夫人耳。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "今子兄弟二十餘人，子又居中，不甚見幸，久質諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "即大王薨，安國君立為王，則子毋幾得與長子及諸子旦暮在前者爭為太子矣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "子楚曰：「然。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "為之柰何？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "呂不韋曰：「子貧，客於此，非有以奉獻於親及結賓客也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "不韋雖貧，請以千金為子西游，事安國君及華陽夫人，立子為適嗣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "子楚乃頓首曰：「必如君策，請得分秦國與君共之。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Zichu was Qin various concubine descendants, hostage among feudal lords, chariot riding expenses not plentiful, dwelling poor, not pleased. Lü Buwei traded Handan, saw and pitied him, said 'This rare goods can store.' Thus went saw Zichu, persuaded saying: 'I can enlarge your gate.' Zichu laughed saying: 'First enlarge your lord's gate, then enlarge my gate!' Lü Buwei said: 'You do not know. My gate waits for your gate to enlarge.' Zichu heart knew meaning, thus led him sit, deeply spoke. Lü Buwei said: 'Qin king aged, Anguo Jun can become crown prince. I secretly heard Anguo Jun loves favors Huayang Madame, Huayang Madame has no sons, can establish proper heir is only Huayang Madame. Now your brothers twenty plus persons, you again middle position, not much favored, long hostage among lords. If great king dies, Anguo Jun establishes as king, then you few chance to contend with eldest son and various sons day night before as crown prince.' Zichu said: 'Yes. Handle how?' Lü Buwei said: 'You poor, guest here, no means to present to parents and tie guests. Buwei though poor, request with thousand jin gold for you west travel, serve Anguo Jun and Huayang Madame, establish you as proper heir.' Zichu thus bowed head: 'Must like your plan, please divide Qin state share with you.'",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "呂不韋乃以五百金與子楚，為進用，結賓客；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "而復以五百金買奇物玩好，自奉而西游秦，求見華陽夫人姊，而皆以其物獻華陽夫人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "因言子楚賢智，結諸侯賓客遍天下，常曰「楚也以夫人為天，日夜泣思太子及夫人」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "夫人大喜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "不韋因使其姊說夫人曰：「吾聞之，以色事人者，色衰而愛弛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "今夫人事太子，甚愛而無子，不以此時蚤自結於諸子中賢孝者，舉立以為適而子之，夫在則重尊，夫百歲之後，所子者為王，終不失勢，此所謂一言而萬世之利也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "不以繁華時樹本，即色衰愛弛後，雖欲開一語，尚可得乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "今子楚賢，而自知中男也，次不得為適，其母又不得幸，自附夫人，夫人誠以此時拔以為適，夫人則竟世有寵於秦矣。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "華陽夫人以為然，承太子閒，從容言子楚質於趙者絕賢，來往者皆稱譽之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "乃因涕泣曰：「妾幸得充後宮，不幸無子，願得子楚立以為適嗣，以託妾身。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "安國君許之，乃與夫人刻玉符，約以為適嗣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "安國君及夫人因厚餽遺子楚，而請呂不韋傅之，子楚以此名譽益盛於諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Lü Buwei thus with five hundred jin gold gave Zichu, for expenses, tie guests; Again with five hundred jin gold bought rare objects curios, personally carried west travel Qin, seek see Huayang Madame sister, all with objects presented Huayang Madame. Thus spoke Zichu worthy wise, ties feudal lord guests fill world, often said 'Zichu takes Madame as heaven, day night weep think crown prince and Madame.' Madame greatly pleased. Buwei thus made her sister persuade Madame saying: 'I heard, serve others with beauty, beauty declines love relaxes. Now Madame serves crown prince, much loved yet no sons, not with this time early self-attach to various sons' worthy filial ones, recommend establish as proper to son him, husband alive then heavy honored, husband hundred years after, sonned becomes king, end not lose power, this called one word ten thousand generations benefit. Not with flourishing time plant roots, then beauty declines love relaxes after, though wish open one word, still obtainable? Now Zichu worthy, self knows middle son, cannot become proper, mother again not favored, self-attaches Madame, Madame truly with this time pull establish as proper, Madame then compete lifetime favored in Qin.' Huayang Madame considered correct, seized crown prince leisure, leisurely spoke Zichu hostage in Zhao extremely worthy, passers all praise him. Thus because wept saying: 'Concubine fortunately fill rear palace, unfortunately no sons, wish Zichu establish as proper heir, to entrust concubine body.' Anguo Jun permitted, thus with Madame engraved jade tally, agreed as proper heir. Anguo Jun and Madame thus thick gifts sent Zichu, requested Lü Buwei tutor him, Zichu with this fame reputation increasingly flourishing among feudal lords.",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "呂不韋取邯鄲諸姬絕好善舞者與居，知有身。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "子楚從不韋飲，見而說之，因起為壽，請之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "呂不韋怒，念業已破家為子楚，欲以釣奇，乃遂獻其姬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "姬自匿有身，至大期時，生子政。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "子楚遂立姬為夫人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Lü Buwei took Handan various beauties extremely good skilled dance with lived, knew had pregnancy. Zichu from Buwei drank, saw pleased, thus rose toast, requested her. Lü Buwei angered, thought already ruined family for Zichu, wished to fish rare, thus presented his beauty. Beauty self hid pregnancy, to great period time, bore son Zheng. Zichu thus established beauty as Madame.",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "秦昭王五十年，使王齮圍邯鄲，急，趙欲殺子楚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "子楚與呂不韋謀，行金六百斤予守者吏，得脫，亡赴秦軍，遂以得歸。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "趙欲殺子楚妻子，子楚夫人趙豪家女也，得匿，以故母子竟得活。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "秦昭王五十六年，薨，太子安國君立為王，華陽夫人為王后，子楚為太子。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "趙亦奉子楚夫人及子政歸秦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen",
          "model": "grok-1.5",
          "literal": "Qin King Zhao fiftieth year, sent Wang Ji besiege Handan, urgent, Zhao wished kill Zichu. Zichu with Lü Buwei planned, gave gold six hundred jin to guard officials, got escape, fled join Qin army, thus able return. Zhao wished kill Zichu wife children, Zichu Madame Zhao powerful family girl, got hide, thus mother child finally survived. Qin King Zhao fifty-sixth year, died, crown prince Anguo Jun established as king, Huayang Madame as queen, Zichu as crown prince. Zhao also sent Zichu Madame and Zi Zheng return Qin.",
          "idiomatic": null
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "秦王立一年，薨，謚為孝文王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-1.5",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
